{"tid":309123,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(圍爐)有冇人都返工返到心灰意冷","createTime":"2017-07-04T17:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T09:47:25.000Z","uid":67297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f69ab2ef932b72cf822fa38d86b7612902163292","tid":309123,"uid":67297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:30:09.000Z","msg":"小弟大學畢業出黎做野整整一年，還咗幾個月學債，重有15年還。日日返工就有返工冇收工，份工又忙又食腦，每日收工好似考完試咁，返到屋企食個冷飯，沖個涼抖下就上得床，有時重要打下report/logbook，根本冇曬個人生活。<br />\n同年嘅朋友，冇讀書，出黎做野三四年。有紀律部隊有工程有金融，好多都人工高過我，準時返工放工，又唔忙又多假。我唯一可以安慰下自己嘅就係自己都算係個&quot;准&quot;專業人事，係人工唔高姐。<br />\n唉，眼見咁就覺得好灰，讀咁多書，專科，點解人工可以低過個啲紀律部隊咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我都係啱啱打完report 想訓前上黎呻下咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675a6f1060474406485309fd09509a4c8450ee3b","tid":309123,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:31:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ff56ad534f6b360ea3d24532fe88f79e3c8a0a7","tid":309123,"uid":67297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:32:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>engine<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841300729f724284677bf52954db4ec2c42b73ba","tid":309123,"uid":54990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>engine<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nconsultant?"},{"pid":"1d80adba174b433127d9dcf5c2aa34a671b68719","tid":309123,"uid":16273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:35:34.000Z","msg":"先岩岩出黎做果一年野，做多幾年野，轉多幾次工，先黎做比較同呻啦"},{"pid":"79ea3a1fd7a0ec0682d1c5a18b7bedca85af4f91","tid":309123,"uid":1559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:35:55.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b13dee0fdff55a93772320f04cfb39dbd04476c","tid":309123,"uid":67297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:43:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827080e044f6ca97d33f25d8c21e7d34fa79bd69","tid":309123,"uid":100935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:53:30.000Z","msg":"踏唔出嗰comfort zone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9029dee4f6f91b576b4f26e5e58dd4334e5aa217","tid":309123,"uid":16029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:14:13.000Z","msg":"你又知人地輕鬆<br />\n唔好覺得得自己辛苦"},{"pid":"85e164a31d4b606bf7d45b6e28034be452c895d1","tid":309123,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你又知人地輕鬆<br />\n唔好覺得得自己辛苦</blockquote><br />\n連登開鬥慘post冇下限，永遠都可以搵到人慘過自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f503e85c77c90ebff9a3cda64d9dea234d3e2c36","tid":309123,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:47:25.000Z","msg":"巴打頂住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}